<subSubSection id="4D5B3A48E0728A4E9BE145D231795EF3" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="conservation status">
<paragraph id="82007811DBAC46C63E14F486DEE452B1" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Conservation status in Cameroon.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8EF1545FD691853F29E3D33BA55C7E14" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName id="7F2AF5601EEBC84569140B77C2771730" authorityName="Bremek., Verh. Kon. Ned. Akad. Wetensch, Afd. Natuurk., Sect. 2. 48 (2): 21" authorityYear="1952" baseAuthorityName="Hiern" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Virectaria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Virectaria angustifolia" order="Gentianales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="angustifolia">
<emphasis id="ACD5F43E0A82839DB9E9A6292EEB0628" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Virectaria angustifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not listed on http://www.iucnredlist.org, nor assessed by 
<bibRefCitation id="F7F2E7F5A649BF72EAC4CA8F7191B45E" author="Onana, JM" journalOrPublisher="Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B66" refString="Onana, JM, Cheek, M, 2011. Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" title="Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments." year="2011">Onana and Cheek (2011)</bibRefCitation>
. The taxon is currently known from more than 7 localities. The extent of occurrence of the species is about 66,500 km2, and its area of occupancy is about 28 km2. Timber exploitation and plantation development are in progress at the collecting localities. Based on these threats and the continuous decline of vegetation cover in the area, extent and /or quality of habitat 
<taxonomicName id="A5DF6AAE30831F375974E02E1951D0E9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Sapindaceae" genus="V." higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="V. angustifolia" order="Sapindales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="angustifolia">
<emphasis id="F7AE25C8B80AEF5BA812B7C6CEADDB34" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">V. angustifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here assessed as Vulnerable. IUCN Red List Category: 
<emphasis id="29A6EE7A03B43B2ACD16A5907E5BF6EF" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Vulnerable VB1+2ab (ii, iii).</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
